  "text": "Skip to content\nSERVICES\nCAPABILITY\nABOUT US\nBLOG\nPARTS GALLERY\nContact Us\nInstant Quoting\n\nUpload a STEP file and receive a reference manufacturing estimate. Final pricing is confirmed after engineering review.\n\nchecking\nPART & PROCESS\nChoose STEP files\n.stp / .step · multiple files · max 50 MB each\nMaterial\nProcess\nLoading…\nGeneral Tolerance\nLoading…\nPostprocess\nLoading…\nQuantity\nCurrency\nUSD\n\nLooking for more material grades, custom materials, machining processes, or finishing options? Contact our engineers for a fast formal review.\n\nContact Details (optional)\nHow should we address you? (optional)\nEmail Address (optional)\nAdd your email if you want our engineers to follow up with a formal quote.\nCalculate Current Part\n\nBy submitting this form, you confirm that you are authorized to share the uploaded file. If you provide contact details, we use them only to generate and follow up on your manufacturing estimate. We treat uploaded drawings and quote data as confidential business information.\n\nPART PREVIEW\nAwaiting STEP analysis.\nREFERENCE ESTIMATE\nSelect parameters and calculate after upload.\n\nProvide you with the best solution according to your requirments and make it easy for you to get parts!\n\ngreat@mfg-solution.com\n\nIndustries\nAutomation\nAutomotive\nElectronic Assemble\nCommunication Device\nMedical Device\nRobotics\nSpare Parts\nCustom Parts\nServices\nCold Forging\nSwiss Lathe\nAuto Lathe\nCNC Machining\n5 Axis CNC Machining\nSheet Metal\nCompression Molding\n3D printing\nContact Us\n\nNeed help or have a question?\nEmail:\n\ngreat@mfg-solution.com\n\nGet A Quote Now !\n\nCopyright © 2026 - MFG SOLUTION Co., Limited ",
